{"tid":2350812,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「集思廣益 」究竟點先算係真·黃絲？黃絲有冇客觀標準？哲學討論？","createTime":"2021-01-02T15:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T19:44:03.000Z","uid":366201,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7ae1dceb9b5d278cec77fd7b414fa09c5f6db38a","tid":2350812,"uid":366201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"如果一個人有去遊行丶有去抗爭<br />\n但附近一近黃店都冇，走去食M記、大家樂或者太興，咁佢究竟仲係唔係黃絲？<br />\n或者如果一個人只係自稱係黃絲，支持黃絲嘅信念同訴求，但就一次遊行同抗爭都冇去過，咁究竟仲係唔係黃？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實黃店都一樣，如果只係喺612 表過1次態，之後就再冇表態，咁仲係唔係黃？"},{"pid":"9ffb9754d909a2b2b8735d04fc508e5299c9ff03","tid":2350812,"uid":123189,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:52:16.000Z","msg":"真正既黃絲就係要活係幻想之中<br />\n就像一場多重夢 無限地輪迴  <br />\n<br />\n政棍吊住舊蘿蔔<br />\n黃絲做馬仔不斷追就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70981d273a2a1a7c8f2c706ebde4ce8c934c6732","tid":2350812,"uid":55091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:24:27.000Z","msg":"要分黃絲嘅原因<br />\n都係想大家互相支持 條路可以行落去<br />\n即使互有批評 個心都係支持對方<br />\n如果唔係抱住想互相支持嘅心態<br />\n分黎做咩<br />\n或者調返轉咁講<br />\n只要你覺得會支持你嘅人 佢哋就係黃絲<br />\n至於乜嘢係你覺得<br />\n每個人都唔同<br />\n你覺得A會支持你<br />\n另一個人又覺得A唔會支持你<br />\n咁你信你自己定另一個人？<br />\n你信唔信A真心支持你？<br />\n講到尾都係個信字<br />\n有咩標準令人信任每個都唔同<br />\n<br />\n當然都可以呼籲人唔好繼續信任另一個人<br />\n但呢個係另一個話題"},{"pid":"f36be8e92ec68827b7ca315884069ecf241543d8","tid":2350812,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:35:42.000Z","msg":"這是種沒有教會的信仰，所以沒有人能&ldquo;認證&rdquo;誰是誰非。"},{"pid":"474e9742498ed56578c4d9ca8d2a25f7607f4150","tid":2350812,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:38:23.000Z","msg":"只要支持五大訴求缺一不可就係黃絲。"},{"pid":"418d2410621140b50b72e799c6a162e40169538e","tid":2350812,"uid":49057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:11:48.000Z","msg":"無客觀標準，但有大概相似嘅訴求同信念<br />\n單憑一兩句有做乜無做乜其實判斷唔到黃唔黃，背景資料太少，行動理由都唔清晰<br />\n而且黃唔黃都未必可以由他人決定，他人決定都未必正確"},{"pid":"15c9bbe7b0cf972184deeac9d2be28ffef189d49","tid":2350812,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:43:00.000Z","msg":"睇返天琦講「教條主義」先再討論啦"},{"pid":"fa2d801321c6ae5f4ed8ed94cd7569df36bd0177","tid":2350812,"uid":62259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T19:44:03.000Z","msg":"要無條件付出/盲撐對自己方有利既野<br />\n做唔足就係偽黃/藍絲<br />\n偽黃仲衰過藍<br />\n比人發現左就準備比人批鬥啦"}]}